name: Ciquette
tagline: A chrome extension for creating d3 visualizations from highlighted text!
body:
# Ciquette
A chrome extension for creating D3 visualizations from highlighted text!

![Example](http://g.recordit.co/uw9Mf9VhAq.gif)

Now that annoying HTML table can be put to work to actually make sense of data.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
